	\arrow["{\text{id}_u}", Rightarrow, from=3, to=2]
\end{tikzcd}\]
we have $\id_u * \id_f = \id_{uf}$. There is some more to be said about this definition, but for the purposes of this appendix we have defined a 2-category in sufficient generality.
\end{definition}
